                            <p><span style="font-size: large;"><strong>Tufted</strong></span></p>
                            <p><span style="font-size: large;">This finish is ideal if you want to prevent loose fillings from being removed or dislodged during usage. Frequently used with pocket sprung mattresses, tapes are placed all around the mattress at regular intervals to make it much more secure. This is known as tufting and will result in a firmer feel.&nbsp;</span></p>
