                            <p><span style="font-size: large;"><strong>Divan Bases</strong></span></p>
                            <p><span style="font-size: large;">Made of two connecting pieces, the divan base is ideal for all types of mattresses, whether deep or not. Usually there are no springs in the base, so the support it provides is quite sturdy.</span></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
