                            <p><span style="font-size: large;">Choosing the correct mattress for a bed frame can be slightly trickier than for a divan base. The mattress may sit on top of or into a frame. In the latter case, it is important that the correct measurements are taken from inside the frame where the mattress will sit. Also, please ensure the headboard has enough height, and does not get hidden if the mattress bought is too deep.</span></p>
